reviews.review_text: - Excellent show, and the La Bamba is an extra special treat. Never heard Garcia do mariachi before. He's a natural!

One of the best late 80s show ever I remember some tie-dye philly guy making shirts in a garage in Santa Cruz took three duffel bags of freshly died Hanes Ts. with XXL sizes and came back loaded with cash and this tape. Mope you are doing well Mikey this is a colieseum grade show rarely scene in Xalifornia.
